snippet.textDisplay: To all the people saying the song sounds like Thunder by Imagine Dragons: Thunder itself sounds like some older songs...Paper Planes by MIA being the most obvious example that comes to mind. Anyway, Atif and Abdullah are both very talented individuals in their own ways and I can't help but feel that their collab could have delivered much more on the whole. The part after 3:45 is what will keep me coming back.
